{"type": "article", "id": 13162, "title": "Disney“Young At Heart”个性定制款", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-07T07:28:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002520tLf9liCMuXkUseP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tDisney 和 Vans 之前发布的 “Young At Heart” 系列近日又出新招，它们在原来的基础上新增加的粮款图案，一款是白底色配卡通人物米奇和，另一款则是粉色配米妮。更重要的是，它们现在推出了个人定制化的 “Young At Heart” 系列，款式有 Vans SK8-Hi，Slip on 和 Old Skool II 背包等等，<a href=\"http://www.vans.com/customs?cm_mmc=LinkShare-_-Affiliate-_-je6NUbpObpQ-_-335851&amp;utm_source=linkshare&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=je6NUbpObpQ\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以定制属于自己的 “Young At Heart”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408080jY1cUVgxN6AqHFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140809Sp2iNvJIOnhtU7Zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140809WQs5JrM9f8YCVhol.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}